{
  "stem": "9503.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I can stand there now and say, oh, boy, this is holding me up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got to be at work, which is a normal response.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Every once in a while, there's still something that'll flash it on unexpectedly, and-- and that I can't handle very well.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went back to Westerbork this past May, because that's the first time that I was able to-- to do that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I am not able, yet, to go to the Holocaust Museum.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- I just don't want to be surprised by anything that I'm not protected against.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you know, I know there's still some very sensitive spots about this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] But by and large, people do not know my history, you know, people in my work life or-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I think, you know, some of our friends treat it probably very respectfully.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You don't get intrusive questions, and I like it that way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I really-- the idea of having to spend the rest of my life with this weighing me down is a-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] it-- it's a horrible thought, you know.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- in a way, I almost have to look forward.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And most of the time I do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What is your relationship to Judaism today?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Really mixed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I said, it took me a good 20 years to say the Kaddish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I have a real push-pull relationship.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't be blindly Orthodox anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I question.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oddly enough, my son, when he-- he became bar mitzvah, his speech consisted strictly of questions, why?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why did God let this happen?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
